calcium channel. Although we can offer no channel model
which results in this I-V relation, it does give a reasonable
fit to the experimental I-V curves (Fig. 2) in Rorsman and
Trube. The shape is much closer to the experimental curves
than that of a linear I-V relation, and the scale is within a
factor of l/3. In particular, for the case [Ca]o = 2.56 mM, it
reproduces the early peak and sharp dropoff in the calcium
current. This representation does not, however, adequately

