In order to carry out a simulation we must choose values
for the number of channels, N,.,, and for either ro or rc.
Based on a density of -1 K-Ca channel per 1 jAm2 patch we
let NtO = 600. For an assumed single-channel conductance
g of 50 pS the total cell conductance gK-Ca is 30,000 pS.
