-5 ms. We have no data on ro for the K-Ca channel in the
,B-cell, but 5 ms. is compatible with data for rat muscle
(Moczydlowski and Latorre, 1983). Finally, the calcium
dissociation constant, Kd, is chosen to be 100 ,uM in order
that Cai will be in the physiological range of -0.5 gM. The
